Update: The gradient at x=0 for function above is not the same as log sigmoid. I just add an additional term to eliminate the difference.
def log_sigmoid(x):
    return torch.clamp(x, max=0) - torch.log(torch.exp(-torch.abs(x)) + 1) + 0.5 * torch.clamp(x, min=0, max=0)
